Swiss Re Hires USAA’s Eric Smith to Lead Americas Division

-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 
2011-06-15T15:11:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-15/swiss-re-hires-usaa-s-eric-smith-to-lead-americas-division.html
Swiss Reinsurance Co., the world’s
second-largest reinsurer, hired J.  Eric Smith  to lead its
Americas business, replacing Pierre Ozendo.  Smith joins from USAA Life Insurance Co., the Zurich-based
reinsurer said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Frye in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  